{"tid":1873742,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人老母用錢概念係零？","createTime":"2020-02-10T20:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T07:36:24.000Z","uid":213295,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"59b835977b744a1d820872c626d8dca3e489aef6","tid":1873742,"uid":213295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T20:46:42.000Z","msg":"首先屋企已經拎緊綜緩 <br />\n4000左右 2個人分 (佢加啊婆)(我估大概<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n然後最近仲要搬屋 大概裝修費,傢俬 最少都要6萬左右<br />\n乜撚傢俬都未買 鋪地下間房啲錢都未撚比哂<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">今日</span></strong></span>老母竟然同我講想買個<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">日本還原水機</span></span> 淨化屋企啲水<br />\n仲要舊野成3萬蚊！佢話要問人借住錢買左先<br />\n其實已經要用我學生資助交剩啲生活費買傢俬<br />\n<br />\n救命 叫又叫過佢幾次唔好買 又唔撚聽人講<br />\n究竟先可以成功馴服老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7091bc61cc3f5af85bd406aeff363738c8120e95","tid":1873742,"uid":213295,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T20:49:51.000Z","msg":"重點係佢之前已經成日買啲野返黎用唔夠5次就放屋企角落種菇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似買個打蛋器，方便煲粥個啲 件件過千 永遠三分鐘熱度"},{"pid":"ce8ec86a16a50e44fb4751eef9941b1a3f070e96","tid":1873742,"uid":304623,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T20:50:47.000Z","msg":"直接屌鳩佢"},{"pid":"d52d8454ba8295c63474529e5d47f35a74590fc0","tid":1873742,"uid":304623,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T20:51:18.000Z","msg":"三萬蚊，我落去買多幾支屈臣氏蒸餾水都唔使咁多錢啦"},{"pid":"b73b5f795c719e76b2bce2a1f59ccd34a11042de","tid":1873742,"uid":87571,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T20:52:22.000Z","msg":"4000蚊 你阿媽同阿婆用，咁你哋仲有冇其他收入？<br />\n如果冇我唔明點樣可以儲到10萬蚊出嚟裝修加買淨水器。"},{"pid":"2b2d494040f8cf17e351c984f9aa2e0aa816c944","tid":1873742,"uid":213295,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"ce8ec86a16a50e44fb4751eef9941b1a3f070e96","tid":1873742,"uid":304