<br />\n我諗我月入40000都冇你阿媽咁揮霍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T21:06:41.000Z","msg":"拎綜緩 電費水費又有得平 公屋房費又有仆街政府貼<br />\n搬屋費社工又申請到一萬 整地下 電視又有得申請一部全新<br />\n老母仲要有返教會 每個月教會仲補貼比啲綜緩人士 生活困難既長者 比人地啲奉獻錢我地<br />\n其實老母真係生活好難差。。"},{"pid":"0ac98d33922b6655dec8a940d67ab3cd5bf0681c","tid":1873742,"uid":235174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T21:07:45.000Z","msg":"伯母係唔係靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44943de3fca91f61de3286c2e602e79cb69fddd8","tid":1873742,"uid":213295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T21:08:04.000Z","msg":"好撚驚佢借財仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c93e861155e22a339e075c8965d9d09d075ce4f0","tid":1873742,"uid":213295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ac98d33922b6655dec8a940d67ab3cd5bf0681c","tid":1873742,"uid":235174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T21:07:45.000Z","msg":"伯母係唔係靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T21:08:56.000Z","msg":"有意領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"ad3c3d00ef5f04b0f8c5fb8baf9a1def458f42ff","tid":1873742,"uid":304623,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T21:12:48.000Z","msg":"為免這樣的事再發生多一次，請你現在立刻到超市購買10罐豆豉鯪魚， 15罐沙甸魚或五香肉丁與20罐午餐肉（更狠可以考慮嘉頓雜餅，但不建議，核爆會波及隔離的）然後告訴你老母，我們沒有多餘的錢了，接下來的一個月、兩個月、三個月的早餐、午餐、晚餐，都要過吃豆豉鯪魚、沙甸魚、午餐肉的日子了，而這都是因為你買了三萬元的淨水器所致，還要提醒她煮飯時不要開大火，因為我們已沒有錢交煤氣費。"},{"pid":"ebe829d2890c31c114c1972e6e3fdfab3622c008","tid":1873742,"uid":304623,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dbfb93879f3d33f25a3ed748cb252189e39450ab","tid":1873742,"uid":213295,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0085607a90bf82997beb08eb1a65f6e96e33da81","tid":1873742,"uid":127454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"